data.description: **Price Adjustment**    Spacious Corner Lot Oasis in Desirable Corner Lake Estates  Welcome to your new haven in the sought-after community of Corner Lake Estates. This impressive residence boasts an expansive corner lot and a wealth of features that will make you feel right at home.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a charming dining area featuring elegant barn doors, setting the tone for the home's character. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream with its spacious layout, island, and not one but two walk-in pantries. French doors open to reveal a screened-in, solar-heated pool area—a perfect spot for entertaining and relaxation. Your new home includes a separate washer/dryer room, complete with the washer and dryer, offering added convenience. Enjoy the abundance of natural light in the generous family room, creating a warm and inviting space for gatherings and everyday living. There's an additional room that can be transformed into an office, playroom, or even an extra bedroom to suit your needs. Upstairs, the master suite features two spacious walk-in closets, a garden tub, a stand-up shower, and a private toilet area, providing a serene retreat. Three more spacious bedrooms upstairs share a full bathroom, ensuring comfort for the whole family.    Recent Upgrades:  New Roof (2021)  New AC Unit (2020)  Freshly Painted Interior (2023)  New Pool Decking (2020)  Brand New Flooring (Stairs and Up Stairs) (2023)  Exterior Paint Updated (2020)    Community Amenities:  Residents of Corner Lake Estates enjoy access to an array of amenities, including a playground, picnic area, and a basketball court. The community is conveniently located near UCF, Full Sail University, and downtown, making it a breeze to explore the city's offerings. Plus, shopping and dining options are just a stone's throw away.    Don't miss the opportunity to call this incredible property home. Contact us today to schedule your private tour and experience the lifestyle that Corner Lake Estates has to offer.    Virtual walkthrough video link: https://youtu.be/S-n-BhFmTqg
